1358171855.text: "Downstream effectors of the PI3K pathway include AKT (protein kinase B), a serine threonine kinase, directly activated by PI3K and the mTOR (mammalian target of rapamycin), another serine threonine kinase leading to an increased translation of various mRNAs encoding cell cycle regulators, including MYC and cyclin D1 and a potential target of therapeutic inhibition."
